<script type="text/javascript" language="javascript">
var dataView = document.getElementById('dataView');
var callbackHashString = '';

function switchLayout(newLayout)
{
	dataView.className = "inventoryList " + newLayout;
	if(callbackHashString && callbackHashString.Length > 1)
	{
		window.location.hash = callbackHashString;
	}
	
	createCookie(_illName, newLayout, 30); 
	
	setTimeout("updateVideoLinks();", 1);
}

function updateVideoLinks()
{
	$$(".itemVideo").each(function(div){
		var divHeight = div.style.height;
		div.style.height = "1 px";
		div.style.height = divHeight;
	});
}

var _illName = 'wmxILL';
var _layout = readCookie(_illName);
if (_layout)
{
	switchLayout(_layout);
}

function createCookie(name,value,days)
{
	if (days)
 	{
  		var date = new Date();
  		date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
  		var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
 	}
 	else
	{
 		var expires = "";
	}

	document.cookie = name+"="+value+expires+"; path=/";
}

function readCookie(name)
{
	var nameEQ = name + "=";
 	var ca = document.cookie.split(';');

 	for(var i=0;i < ca.length;i++)
 	{
  		var c = ca[i];
  		while (c.charAt(0)==' ') c = c.substring(1,c.length);
  		if (c.indexOf(nameEQ) == 0) return c.substring(nameEQ.length,c.length);
 	}

 	return null;
}

function eraseCookie(name) 
{
	createCookie(name,"",-1);
}

var oldRow = null;
function inventoryrow_onmouseover(o, InventoryId, imagePath, imageText)
{
	if (o != oldRow)
	{
		var hoverRow = new cmxElement();
		
		if (oldRow != null)
		{
			hoverRow.setElement(oldRow);
			hoverRow.swapStyle('', false);
		}
	
		oldRow = o;
		hoverRow.setElement(o);
		hoverRow.swapStyle('selecteditem', true);

		var thumbnailContainer = new cmxElement();
		thumbnailContainer.setId("ThumbnailContainer");

		if (imagePath != "NoPhoto")
		{
			thumbnailContainer.element.innerHTML = "<img src='" + imagePath + "' class='thumbnailImage'><div class='thumbnailText'>" + imageText + "</div>";
		}
		else
		{
			thumbnailContainer.element.innerHTML = "<img src='http://images.webmakerx.net/ControlLibrary/Consumer/Special/Photo_Coming_Soon.png' class='thumbnailImage'>";
		}
		
		var priceText = o.getElementsByTagName("div")[0].innerHTML;
		thumbnailContainer.element.innerHTML = thumbnailContainer.element.innerHTML + "<div class='mainPrice'>" + priceText + "</div>";
		
		var browserType = new cmxBrowser();
		var offset = 6;
		
		if (browserType.safari == true)
		{
			offset = 5;
		}
		else if (browserType.ie == true)
		{
			offset = 8;
		}
		
		thumbnailContainer.style.top = parseInt(hoverRow.element.offsetTop - (hoverRow.height / 2) -offset) + "px";
		thumbnailContainer.style.left = "0";
		thumbnailContainer.show();
	}
}

function CompareBoxChange(element)
{
	checkBox = element;
	lineViewCompares = $$('table.inventory .checkbox input');
	blockViewCompares = $$('.compareArea .checkbox input');
	lineViewNumber = lineViewCompares.indexOf(checkBox);
	
	if (lineViewNumber > -1)
	{
		blockViewCompares[lineViewNumber].checked = checkBox.checked;
	}
	else
	{
		blockViewNumber = blockViewCompares.indexOf(checkBox);
		lineViewCompares[blockViewNumber].checked = checkBox.checked;
	}
}

function cancelEvent(e)
{
	if (!e)
	{
		var e = window.event;
	}
	e.cancelBubble = true;
	if (e.stopPropagation)
	{
		e.stopPropagation();
	}
}
